         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"An account rendered to the heirs of Hippias:;I received through the bank of Chrysaphios        2000 dr.;                     "                     "                 "  Antonius                2400 dr.;                     "                     "                 "  Dioskoros;                     of the rents which they owed                     112 dr.;                     Total   4512 dr.    Remainder . . .";(Verso): "Receipt . . ."</ab>
